OL,3,CReading, writing and wrestling -
OL,4,CTeacher swaps classroom for wrestling
OL,5,Cring
OL,7,FA teacher-turned professional
OL,8,Fwrestler, is bringing the heat to his
OL,9,FYear 3 classrooms, where he teaches
OL,10,Fthe four Rs - reading, writing,
OL,11,Farithmetic and wrestling
OL,13,FOutside of the ring, Carl Restall,
OL,14,Ffrom Hampshire, teaches his pupils at
OL,15,FDenmead Primary School. However,
OL,16,Finside the ring, he turns into Karl
OL,17,FAtlas, a wrestler who rides the ropes
OL,18,Fand takes down his opponents.
