OL,3,CReading, writing and wrestling -
OL,4,CTeacher swaps classroom for wrestling
OL,5,Cring
OL,7,FHe has now combined his two loves for
OL,8,Fa force of good, raising money for
OL,9,Fcharity, running a wrestling event,
OL,10,Fwhere the profits go towards new
OL,11,Fclassroom equipment.
OL,13,FMr Restall believes that a lot of the
OL,14,Fskills he uses to teach his 7 and 8-
OL,15,Fyear-old pupils also help him to
OL,16,Fcaptivate a wrestling audience.
