OL,3,CReading, writing and wrestling -
OL,4,CTeacher swaps classroom for wrestling
OL,5,Cring
OL,7,F"I think there is a lot of cross over
OL,8,Fthere. Being adaptive and being able
OL,9,Fto change on the fly, you never know
OL,10,Fhow an audience is going to react,
OL,11,Fsame as you never know how a class is
OL,12,Fgoing to react," he said
OL,14,F"Once upon a time you would call it
OL,15,Fattention-seeking. I call it
OL,16,Fconnection seeking. I think good
OL,17,Fteachers seek a connection with their
OL,18,Fclass and good wrestlers seek a
OL,19,Fconnection with their audience.
