OL,3,CReading, writing and wrestling -
OL,4,CTeacher swaps classroom for wrestling
OL,5,Cring
OL,7,F"Teachers need to have a presence;
OL,8,Fthey need to fill a room.
OL,10,F"They need to command a room the same
OL,11,Fas wrestlers, to take the audience on
OL,12,Fthat emotional journey. Whereas
OL,13,Fteachers take their kids on a learning
OL,14,Fjourney."
OL,16,FThe Year 3 pupils of the class love Mr
OL,17,FRestall's unique smackdown approach
OL,18,Fand call him 'really kind' who
OL,19,Fsometimes 'can act really funny and
OL,20,Fhe's a really good teacher.'
